  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThere are several issues with this screen:\r\n\r\n1. when scrolling this list (with touchpad) -> the list is hardly scrollable\r\n2. not trivial for user that there is Load More button in the bottom, especially when scrolling is pain\r\n3. when clicking Load More -> no visual effect is happening, so user is not clear on what is the app doing -> is the history being fetched? We can add a \"click\" visual effect (pressed state) for the button and maybe a spinner to show the load is ongoing\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2022-09-08 at 18 56 24\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/189169407-6bb20102-e646-4086-9b00-ff8dd42ab66c.png\">\r\n",
